a)  Change the rotation to a per week baises?  Or leave it as it is now?  (If its changes I would suggest waiting until FoR got called up on a god killing first)<br>
<br>
b)  Members of a BB guild can not be killing in a plane (except on thier own dates) unless they are the BB guild on call.  (This may not be stated clearly, basicaly what Emil said above.)<br>
<br>
c)  Guilds can do as they please with epic loot.<br>
<br>
d)  It was suggested elsewhere that BB guilds could quit being a BB guild just to help someone clear the plane.  So, to head off ths abuse, BB guilds must give 2 week notice before they quit being a BB guild.  Or at least they can not help with a plane clearing for 2 weeks after thet reite from BB status. <br>
<br>
e)  This one goes with rule d.  If a former BB guild wishes to become a BB guild again, they must wait 2 weeks after reapplying, at which point they will be readded at the bottom of the BB rotation.  This means a 4 week lose of BB status for a guild if they quit and then rejoin. <p>Milambus Mandragon<BR>
